  <center><b><u><h2 align="center">SETTLEMENT OFFER</h2></b></u><br></center>
We note that your account is in a seriously delinquent status, and your balance remains unpaid. If your account continues to be neglected in this manner we will need to review for further action against you <br><br>

This is your last opportunity to resolve this matter and clear your account balance owed to {!Product__c.Account_Purchasing_Entity__c} .  <br><br>

To that end, Canaccede Financial  is prepared to discount the balance, on a limited time basis, and accept the sum of<strong> 
{!Product__c.Product_Current_Balance__c}
 </strong>, to close your account as settled in full. This represents a savings of {!Product__c.Product_Current_Balance_2__c}
. <br><br>

Payment <strong>MUST</strong> be <strong>received</strong> on or before <strong>{!TODAY()+14}</strong> , to complete this settlement. Once these funds are received the account will be closed as settled and your credit report will be updated to reflect a settlement has been reached. A Release letter will be issued upon request and confirmation of receipt of funds. <br><br>

Please note, if funds are not received by the <strong>{!TODAY()+14}</strong> the settlement offer will be considered null and void and the full balance will become due immediately (Including all principal and interest).<br><br>

<strong>Choose one of our convenient payment options listed below:</strong><br>
